rows.label: qst104225_msg0002
rows.name:
Rex-sensei, can you easily find
amazing treasure in the Cloud Sea?

rows.label: qst104225_msg0021
rows.name:
Of course! I could probably find
valuable treasure even if I
salvaged with my eyes closed.

rows.label: qst104225_msg0022
rows.name:
Wow! I want to see you
salvage, Rex-sensei!

rows.label: qst104225_msg0041
rows.name:
It's not that easy... You won't
find amazing treasure unless
you dive many, many times.

rows.label: qst104225_msg0042
rows.name:
I see... I thought you just
dived once and came back
with tons of treasure.

rows.label: qst104225_msg0043
rows.name:
I've never seen Rex-sensei
salvage before! Show me!
